      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. CALISTA (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (25.20) last time in a Bottom Up - Grade 6 at this track. Tough to beat if on-song. SURPRISED (6) was in the money two back in a Grade 6 at Bendigo then jumped from a squeeze draw last time and was not far away when third (24.21) over 425m at Bendigo. Expected to do much better this time. BRINDLE MOSAIC (7) is an honest type who is new here. Jumped quickly and was in the firing line throughout when winning last time over 400m at Warragul (23.08). Solid formlines coming through her last run. In great recent form and expected to measure up again. INTENT GAZE (3) hit the frame here last start and can sneak into the finish again.",
